                             Online Permitting

   Welcome to the City of Long Beach online permitting!
   This service is provided to our regular customers who wish to do
   business with the Planning and Building Department without the need to
   visit City Hall. This service will be provided to contractors who have
   an existing accounts receivable with the Department or wish to
   establish one.
